    <title>Android Studio安装教程</title>
    <url>/post/2afc15d8.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h4 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a><strong>前言</strong></h4><p>本博客仅用于个人学习分享，文章内容源于网络整理与个人总结，如有侵权，请联系本人删除！</p>
<h4 id="Android-Studio"><a href="#Android-Studio" class="headerlink" title="Android Studio"></a><code>Android Studio</code></h4><p>Android Studio 是开发 Android 应用程序的官方 <code>IDE</code>，基于 <code>Intellij IDEA</code>。</p>
<ul>
<li><h5 id="下载"><a href="#下载" class="headerlink" title="下载"></a>下载</h5></li>
</ul>
<p>进入<a href="https://developer.android.google.cn/studio/"><code>Andriod Studio</code>官网</a>点击<code>DOWNLOAD ANDROID STUDIO</code>下载。</p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/DeXkM8"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/18/DeXkM8.png"></a></p>
<ul>
<li><h5 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a><strong>安装</strong></h5></li>
</ul>
<p>点击已下载的安装包，逐步进行安装，图示如下：</p>
<p>①点击<code>Next</code></p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/DeXUiR"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/18/DeXUiR.png"></a></p>
<p>②点击<code>Next</code></p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/DeXOWq"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/18/DeXOWq.png"></a></p>
<p>③安装路径建议安装在除<code>C</code>盘以外的地方，更改后点击<code>Next</code></p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/DeXvlV"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/18/DeXvlV.png"></a></p>
<p>④点击<code>Install</code></p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/DeXxyT"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/18/DeXxyT.png"></a></p>
<p>⑤点击<code>Next</code></p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/DeveCn"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/18/DeveCn.png"></a>****</p>
<p>⑥<code>Start Android Studio</code>根据自己需求选择是否启动，然后点击<code>Finish</code></p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Devm3q"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/18/Devm3q.png"></a></p>
<p>⑦第一次安装<code>android studio</code>时候弹出<code>unable to access android sdk add-on list</code>原因是你电脑没有<code>SDK</code>而且你下载的<code>android studio</code>又是不带<code>SDK</code>的，点击<code>Cencel</code>即可进入下一环节</p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Devc8I"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/18/Devc8I.png"></a></p>
<p>⑧此处提示找不到<code>Android SDK</code>，点击<code>Next</code></p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Dex5y6"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/18/Dex5y6.png"></a></p>
<p>⑨更改位置，然后点击<code>Next</code></p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/DexIOK"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/18/DexIOK.png"></a></p>
<p>⑩点击<code>Finish</code></p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Dezpm8"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/18/Dezpm8.png"></a></p>
<p>⑪点击<code>Finish</code>完成安装</p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Dezgnf"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/18/Dezgnf.png"></a></p>
<p>⑫<code>Welcome to Android Studio</code></p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/DmpBQI"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/18/DmpBQI.png"></a></p>
<ul>
<li><h5 id="使用"><a href="#使用" class="headerlink" title="使用"></a><strong>使用</strong></h5></li>
</ul>
<p>①点击<code>Create New Project</code>创建第一个项目</p>
<p>②对相关信息进行配置，点击<code>Next</code></p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Dm90NF"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/18/Dm90NF.png"></a></p>
<p>③项目启动后主界面</p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/DmAJc4"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/18/DmAJc4.png"></a></p>
<p>④<code>Run</code></p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Dm5iZt"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/18/Dm5iZt.png"></a></p>
<h5 id="踩坑指南"><a href="#踩坑指南" class="headerlink" title="踩坑指南"></a><strong>踩坑指南</strong></h5><p>①<code>Build</code>时报错：你的主机中的软件中止了一个已建立的连接。</p>
<p>错因：笔记本打开了移动热点</p>
<p>解决办法：关闭移动热点，重新<code>clean</code></p>
<p>②<code>Session &#39;app&#39;: Installation did not succeed.The application could not be installed: INSTALL FAILED INSUFFICIENT STORAGE Retry</code></p>
<p>错因：<code>Session &#39;app&#39;</code>:安装失败。无法安装应用程序:安装失败，存储空间不足，请重试</p>
<p>解决办法：点击最上面一行菜单栏的<code>Build</code>选项，选择 <code>Clean Project</code>，清理缓存之后，重启<code>Android Studio</code>就好了</p>
]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>Android</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>Hexo + Next主题美化（基于本博客）</title>
    <url>/post/af96d78a.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h4 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h4><p>本博客仅用于个人学习分享，文章内容源于网络整理与个人总结，如有侵权，请联系本人删除！</p>
<h4 id="Next安装配置"><a href="#Next安装配置" class="headerlink" title="Next安装配置"></a><code>Next</code>安装配置</h4><p>在 <code>Hexo</code> 中有2份主要的配置文件，其名称都是<code>_config.yml</code>。 其中，一份位于博客根目录下，主要包含 <code>Hexo</code> 本身的配置；另一份位于<code>themes/next/</code>目录下，用于配置主题相关的选项。</p>
<ul>
<li><h5 id="Next下载安装"><a href="#Next下载安装" class="headerlink" title="Next下载安装"></a><code>Next</code>下载安装</h5></li>
</ul>
<p>进入个人博客根目录 <code>-&gt;</code> 右键选择<code>Git Bash Here</code>输入如下命令：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next themes/next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>安装完成后，点击<code>Themes</code>会发现多出一个<code>Next</code>文件夹，表示<code>Next</code>主题安装成功。 </p>
<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/15/0oO5dK.png"></p>
<ul>
<li><h5 id="Next初步配置"><a href="#Next初步配置" class="headerlink" title="Next初步配置"></a><code>Next</code>初步配置</h5></li>
</ul>
<p>进入个人博客根目录打开<code>_config.yml</code>，更改配置文件如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme: next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>效果图如下：（此处已经是写了文章的款式，大致差不多）</p>
<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/15/0ovE5T.png"></p>
<ul>
<li><h5 id="Next主题风格"><a href="#Next主题风格" class="headerlink" title="Next主题风格"></a><code>Next</code>主题风格</h5></li>
</ul>
<p><code>Next</code>提供了四中主题风格<code>scheme</code>，可以在<code>博客根目录/themes/next/_config.yml</code>主题配置文件中进行选择，分别是：<code>Muse、Mist、Pisces、Gemini</code>（本文以<code>Muse</code>风格作介绍）</p>
<h4 id="Next主题美化"><a href="#Next主题美化" class="headerlink" title="Next主题美化"></a><code>Next</code>主题美化</h4><ul>
<li><h5 id="修改文章显示标签"><a href="#修改文章显示标签" class="headerlink" title="修改文章显示标签"></a>修改文章显示标签</h5></li>
</ul>
<p>标签样式默认为<code>#tag</code>，我们可以将其改成带图标的在<code>博客根目录\themes\next\layout\_macro\post.njk</code>，搜索 <code>&#39;#&#39;</code>，将 <code>#</code> 换成<code>&lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-tag&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;</code></p>
<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/15/0TMjoV.png"></p>
<ul>
<li><h5 id="Fork-Me-On-GitHub"><a href="#Fork-Me-On-GitHub" class="headerlink" title="Fork Me On GitHub"></a><code>Fork Me On GitHub</code></h5></li>
</ul>
<p>点击<a href="https://tholman.com/github-corners/">GitHub Corners</a>选择自己喜欢的样式并复制代码到<code>博客根目录/themes/next/layout/_layout.njk</code>，把刚才复制的代码放入<code>&lt;div class=&quot;headband&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</code>下面，并把<code>href</code>改为自己的<code>GitHub</code>地址。</p>
<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/15/07CWuD.png"></p>
<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/15/07F5E4.png"></p>
<ul>
<li><h5 id="点击出现桃心效果"><a href="#点击出现桃心效果" class="headerlink" title="点击出现桃心效果"></a>点击出现桃心效果</h5></li>
</ul>
<p>在<code>博客根目录/themes/next/source/js</code>下新建文件<code>clicklove.js</code>，接着把下面这段代码拷贝粘贴到<code>clicklove.js</code>文件中。</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">!<span class="keyword">function</span>(e,t,a)&#123;<span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function"><span class="title">n</span></span>()&#123;c(<span class="string">&quot;.heart&#123;width: 10px;height: 10px;position: fixed;background: #f00;transform: rotate(45deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(45deg);-moz-transform: rotate(45deg);&#125;.heart:after,.heart:before&#123;content: &#x27;&#x27;;width: inherit;height: inherit;background: inherit;border-radius: 50%;-webkit-border-radius: 50%;-moz-border-radius: 50%;position: fixed;&#125;.heart:after&#123;top: -5px;&#125;.heart:before&#123;left: -5px;&#125;&quot;</span>),o(),r()&#125;<span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function"><span class="title">r</span></span>()&#123;<span class="keyword">for</span>(var e=0;e&lt;d.length;e++)d[e].alpha&lt;=0?(t.body.removeChild(d[e].el),d.splice(e,1)):(d[e].y--,d[e].scale+=.004,d[e].alpha-=.013,d[e].el.style.cssText=<span class="string">&quot;left:&quot;</span>+d[e].x+<span class="string">&quot;px;top:&quot;</span>+d[e].y+<span class="string">&quot;px;opacity:&quot;</span>+d[e].alpha+<span class="string">&quot;;transform:scale(&quot;</span>+d[e].scale+<span class="string">&quot;,&quot;</span>+d[e].scale+<span class="string">&quot;) rotate(45deg);background:&quot;</span>+d[e].color+<span class="string">&quot;;z-index:99999&quot;</span>);requestAnimationFrame(r)&#125;<span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function"><span class="title">o</span></span>()&#123;var t=<span class="string">&quot;function&quot;</span>==typeof e.onclick&amp;&amp;e.onclick;e.onclick=<span class="keyword">function</span>(e)&#123;t&amp;&amp;t(),i(e)&#125;&#125;<span class="keyword">function</span> i(e)&#123;var a=t.createElement(<span class="string">&quot;div&quot;</span>);a.className=<span class="string">&quot;heart&quot;</span>,d.push(&#123;el:a,x:e.clientX-5,y:e.clientY-5,scale:1,alpha:1,color:s()&#125;),t.body.appendChild(a)&#125;<span class="keyword">function</span> c(e)&#123;var a=t.createElement(<span class="string">&quot;style&quot;</span>);a.type=<span class="string">&quot;text/css&quot;</span>;try&#123;a.appendChild(t.createTextNode(e))&#125;catch(t)&#123;a.styleSheet.cssText=e&#125;t.getElementsByTagName(<span class="string">&quot;head&quot;</span>)[0].appendChild(a)&#125;<span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function"><span class="title">s</span></span>()&#123;<span class="built_in">return</span><span class="string">&quot;rgb(&quot;</span>+~~(255*Math.random())+<span class="string">&quot;,&quot;</span>+~~(255*Math.random())+<span class="string">&quot;,&quot;</span>+~~(255*Math.random())+<span class="string">&quot;)&quot;</span>&#125;var d=[];e.requestAnimationFrame=<span class="function"><span class="title">function</span></span>()&#123;<span class="built_in">return</span> e.requestAnimationFrame||e.webkitRequestAnimationFrame||e.mozRequestAnimationFrame||e.oRequestAnimationFrame||e.msRequestAnimationFrame||<span class="keyword">function</span>(e)&#123;setTimeout(e,1e3/60)&#125;&#125;(),n()&#125;(window,document);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>修改<code>_layout.njk</code>，在<code>博客根目录\themes\next\layout\_layout.njk</code>找个合适的地方添加：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;!-- 页面点击小红心 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;script <span class="built_in">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;text/javascript&quot;</span> src=<span class="string">&quot;/js/clicklove.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/15/07Eqvq.png"></p>
<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/15/07VCG9.png"></p>
<ul>
<li><h5 id="侧边栏图标链接"><a href="#侧边栏图标链接" class="headerlink" title="侧边栏图标链接"></a>侧边栏图标链接</h5></li>
</ul>
<p>打开主题配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>，找到<code>social</code>根据自己的需要来选择，并附上自己的地址链接。</p>
<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/15/07iFJI.png"></p>
<p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/15/07k9PA.png"></p>
<ul>
<li><h5 id="头像设置"><a href="#头像设置" class="headerlink" title="头像设置"></a>头像设置</h5></li>
</ul>
<p>打开主题配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>，找到<code>avatar</code>，在<code>url</code>后添加图片路径。</p>
<ul>
<li><h5 id="文章持久化链接设置"><a href="#文章持久化链接设置" class="headerlink" title="文章持久化链接设置"></a>文章持久化链接设置</h5></li>
</ul>
<p><code>hexo-abbrlink</code>插件，它会自动根据文章时间点生成最终博客文章链接，后期不管怎么修改文章永久链接都不会再变。同时文章链接层级更短，使得博客文章更利于<code>SEO</code>。</p>
<p><strong><code>hexo-abbrlink</code>安装：</strong></p>
<p>在博客根目录使用 <code>git bash</code> 执行命令：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-abbrlink --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong><code>hexo-abbrlink</code>配置：</strong></p>
<p>打开根目录下的 <code>_config.yml</code> 文件，搜索<code>permalink</code>，注释掉之前的配置，修改为如下配置：</p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/DpE78K"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/13/DpE78K.png"></a></p>
<ul>
<li><h5 id="本地搜索"><a href="#本地搜索" class="headerlink" title="本地搜索"></a>本地搜索</h5></li>
</ul>
<p>在博客根目录使用 <code>git bash</code> 执行命令：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-searchdb --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在博客根目录下的<code>/theme/next/_config.yml</code>文件任意位置添加配置：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">search:</span><br><span class="line">  path: search.xml</span><br><span class="line">  field: post</span><br><span class="line">  format: html</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">limit</span>: 10000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在<code>Next</code>主题配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>文件中搜索<code>local_search</code>，将<code>enable</code>改为<code>true</code>：</p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Dpm3qg"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/13/Dpm3qg.png"></a></p>
<p><strong>效果：</strong></p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Dpm4sO"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/13/Dpm4sO.png"></a></p>
<ul>
<li><h5 id="背景动画设置"><a href="#背景动画设置" class="headerlink" title="背景动画设置"></a>背景动画设置</h5></li>
</ul>
<p>①在<code>Next</code>主题根目录使用 <code>git bash</code> 执行<code>canvas_nest module</code>安装命令：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/theme-next/theme-next-canvas-nest <span class="built_in">source</span>/lib/canvas-nest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>②在<code>Next</code>主题根目录<code>_config.yml</code>中任意位置添加如下代码：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">canvas_nest: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>③在博客根目录<code>/source</code>文件夹下创建<code>_data</code>文件夹，在<code>_data</code>文件夹下创建<code>footer.njk</code>文件，写入以下代码，详情请查阅<a href="https://github.com/theme-next/theme-next-canvas-nest">Canvas_nest</a>官方文档（因为在<code>Next 6.0</code>后设置 <code>Canvas_nest: true</code>无反应）：</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script color=<span class="string">&quot;0,0,255&quot;</span> opacity=<span class="string">&quot;0.7&quot;</span> zIndex=<span class="string">&quot;-1&quot;</span> count=<span class="string">&quot;123&quot;</span> src=<span class="string">&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/canvas-nest.js@1/dist/canvas-nest.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>④打开<code>Next</code>主题<code>_config.yml</code>进行如下更改：</p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Dp3fqP"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/13/Dp3fqP.png"></a></p>
<p><strong>效果图：</strong></p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Dp3Orq"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/13/Dp3Orq.png"></a></p>
<ul>
<li><h5 id="侧边栏阅读进度百分比"><a href="#侧边栏阅读进度百分比" class="headerlink" title="侧边栏阅读进度百分比"></a>侧边栏阅读进度百分比</h5></li>
</ul>
<p>在<code>Next</code>主题根目录编辑<code>_config.yml</code>配置文件，更改如下配置：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">back2top:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">enable</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  sidebar: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  scrollpercent: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>效果图：</strong></p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/DprVc6"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/13/DprVc6.png"></a></p>
<ul>
<li><h5 id="图片懒加载设置"><a href="#图片懒加载设置" class="headerlink" title="图片懒加载设置"></a>图片懒加载设置</h5></li>
</ul>
<p>在<code>Next</code>主题根目录编辑<code>_config.yml</code>配置文件，更改如下配置：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">lazyload: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li><h5 id="添加图片放大预览功能"><a href="#添加图片放大预览功能" class="headerlink" title="添加图片放大预览功能"></a>添加图片放大预览功能</h5></li>
</ul>
<p>在<code>Next</code>主题根目录编辑<code>_config.yml</code>配置文件，更改如下配置：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">lazyload: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li><h5 id="文章正文添加阴影框"><a href="#文章正文添加阴影框" class="headerlink" title="文章正文添加阴影框"></a>文章正文添加阴影框</h5></li>
</ul>
<p>①在<code>Next</code>主题根目录编辑<code>_config.yml</code>配置文件，更改如下配置：</p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/Dp7pz8"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/13/Dp7pz8.png"></a></p>
<p>②在博客根目录<code>/source/_data</code>文件夹下创建<code>styles.style</code>文件，写入以下代码：</p>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.post</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="attribute">margin-top</span>: <span class="number">60px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="attribute">margin-bottom</span>: <span class="number">60px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="attribute">padding</span>: <span class="number">25px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="attribute">-webkit-box-shadow</span>: <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">5px</span> <span class="built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="number">202</span>, <span class="number">203</span>, <span class="number">203</span>, .<span class="number">5</span>);</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="attribute">-moz-box-shadow</span>: <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">5px</span> <span class="built_in">rgba</span>(<span class="number">202</span>, <span class="number">203</span>, <span class="number">204</span>, .<span class="number">5</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li><h5 id="代码块复制和高亮设置"><a href="#代码块复制和高亮设置" class="headerlink" title="代码块复制和高亮设置"></a>代码块复制和高亮设置</h5></li>
</ul>
<p>在<code>Next</code>主题根目录编辑<code>_config.yml</code>配置文件，更改如下配置：</p>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/DpHL4I"><img src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2020/11/13/DpHL4I.png"></a></p>
<ul>
<li><h5 id="文章内链接文本样式"><a href="#文章内链接文本样式" class="headerlink" title="文章内链接文本样式"></a>文章内链接文本样式</h5></li>
</ul>
<p>打开<code>Next</code>主题<code>/source/css/_common/components/post/post.styl</code>，在末尾添加如下代码：</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.post-body p a&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  color: #0593d3;</span><br><span class="line">  border-bottom: none;</span><br><span class="line">  border-bottom: 1px solid #0593d3;</span><br><span class="line">  &amp;:hover &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    color: #fc6423;</span><br><span class="line">    border-bottom: none;</span><br><span class="line">    border-bottom: <span class="number">1</span>px solid #fc6423;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li><h5 id="顶部阅读进度条"><a href="#顶部阅读进度条" class="headerlink" title="顶部阅读进度条"></a>顶部阅读进度条</h5></li>
</ul>
<p>在<code>Next</code>主题根目录编辑<code>_config.yml</code>配置文件，更改如下配置：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">reading_progress:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">enable</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  color: <span class="string">&quot;#FF0000&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  height: 2px</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li><h5 id="书签"><a href="#书签" class="headerlink" title="书签"></a>书签</h5></li>
</ul>
<p>在<code>Next</code>主题根目录编辑<code>_config.yml</code>配置文件，更改如下配置：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Bookmark Support</span></span><br><span class="line">bookmark:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">enable</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Customize the color of the bookmark.</span></span><br><span class="line">  color: <span class="string">&quot;#222&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># If auto, save the reading progress when closing the page or clicking the bookmark-icon.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># If manual, only save it by clicking the bookmark-icon.</span></span><br><span class="line">  save: auto</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li><h5 id="页脚Hexo配置"><a href="#页脚Hexo配置" class="headerlink" title="页脚Hexo配置"></a>页脚<code>Hexo</code>配置</h5></li>
</ul>
<p>在<code>Next</code>主题根目录编辑<code>_config.yml</code>配置文件，更改如下配置：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Powered by Hexo &amp; NexT</span></span><br><span class="line">  powered: <span class="literal">false</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
